---
title: Beef Chiles Rellenos with Poblano Peppers and Chipotle Sauce
description: This recipe is all filler, but we mean that in the best possible way. Soft-roasted poblanos are stuffed to the brim with a warmly spiced mix of ground beef and rice, then blanketed with a rich tomato sauce and a layer of melted Monterrey Jack cheese. In other words, it’s got plenty of substance and south-of-the-border style, too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5b76dd3530006c036e19cbf2-0488d579.jpg
